Package com.oracle.tools.deferred.jmx

Interface Summary
DeferredJMXConnector.JMXConnectorBuilder A DeferredJMXConnector.JMXConnectorBuilder provides a mechanism to realize a JMXConnector when required.
 

Class Summary
DeferredJMXConnector A DeferredJMXConnector is a Deferred for a JMXConnector.
DeferredJMXConnector.StandardJMXConnectorBuilder A DeferredJMXConnector.StandardJMXConnectorBuilder is a DeferredJMXConnector.JMXConnectorBuilder implementation that uses standard JMX methods to create a JMXConnector.
DeferredMBeanAttribute<T> A DeferredMBeanAttribute is a Deferred for an MBean attribute.
DeferredMBeanInfo A DeferredMBeanInfo is a Deferred for an MBeanInfo.
DeferredMBeanProxy<T> A DeferredMBeanProxy is a Deferred for a local proxy to an MBean.
